<br>
Modern Mullahs by contrast learn everything they know from a very select list of sources... chief among these is the Koran. Schools throughout the Middles East (Wahabi) &quot;Educate&quot; young boys and girls solely based on the teachings of the Koran. Math, Science, Logic, Reason are taught... briefly and only the things that do not contradict any teachings of the Koran.<br>
<br>
This religion has stagnated. It has not evolved or changed as mankind has changed. The result is a dangerous cancer that spreads only through the destruction of anything around it. Medieval laws are still enforced under Islam with such measures as stoning for marital impropriety, and amputation of limbs with a sword for theft. <br>
<br>
Leaders are not elected by democratic means. Well… I take that back, Iraq just had an election. Big surprise, Sadam one with 99.975 percent of the vote. His bold strategy of controlling all aspects of the election and only having one candidate on the ballot really paid off. In a non-related story .025 percent of the population of Iraq was shot yesterday after the elections. Anyway, under Islam Allah decides who the leader is in the Caliphate. There are factions of Islam that want a separate Caliphate to be formed in the United States (See Farrakhan). In Indonesia the Islamic group that bombed Bali has the stated goal of turning Indonesia into an Islamic Caliphate.<br>
<br>
There was a time in history when Islam was a great idea. Rules like “Don’t eat pork” were excellent in the days before refrigeration. These rules are pointless now because humanity has changed, evolved, and become much more aware of the universe around us. Islam however has not.<br>
